title: Buffy Season Eight #5 - The Chain
description:
PDF Version

The Slayer population of the world has gone from two to nearly two thousand. Almost five hundred are working around the world with Buffy&#039;s organization in squads- or "terrorist cells", according to the American military. To combat the threats that have followed Buffy&#039;s new visibility, two other slayers are scattered around the globe, severing as her decoys.
